id=docker-chroot-selinux
name=Docker Chroot SELinux + Mount
version=v1.0
versionCode=1
author=AlexDev404
description=Persists SELinux policy patches and RW ext4 loop mount for Docker storage inside Alpine chroot-distro. Patches: kernel→system_data_file read/write/open/getattr, system_data_file→system_data_file filesystem associate. Mounts docker-storage.img at /data/local/chroot-distro/alpine/var/lib/docker with context= and --make-shared propagation.
